Spawn an independent worker process. By default uses a built-in agent with {tools} tools. The worker only sees the task description you provide — no conversation history.{opencode_note}{acp_note}

If OpenCode or ACP is enabled and the task is coding-heavy (multi-file edits, debugging, refactors), set `worker_type` to `"opencode"` or `"acp"` and include a `directory`.
